    |   """
    |   NameList:
    |     ts_col TIMESTAMP tumble.ts_col#3
    |     WINDOW_START TIMESTAMP tumble.WINDOW_START#5
    |     WINDOW_END TIMESTAMP tumble.WINDOW_END#6
    |   NameScope:
    |     Names:
    |       WINDOW_END -> TIMESTAMP (tumble.WINDOW_END#6)
    |       WINDOW_START -> TIMESTAMP (tumble.WINDOW_START#5)
    |       ts_col -> TIMESTAMP (tumble.ts_col#3)
    |     Range variables:
